race.comment: MERCATELLO (10) is a Gollan first starter by Snitzel from a Falvelon mare. Won her latest trial by a clear margin over 1000m at Doomben. Looks a ready-to-run type who can open her career in the best possible manner. CRYPTO MISS (9) returns for a second prep after placing at three of five runs in the maiden campaign, all over today's journey. Trialled well at Warwick recently so she looks set for a positive start to this preparation. BOSS MODE (7) is back from a 24-week spell. Opened the maiden prep with a placing in a decent form race at the Gold Coast over this distance. Finished second in a recent Doomben trial. Major player with Maloney to pilot. Bivouac debutant YARANGA (5) is bound to create interest after winning his only two public trials. Trained here and draws a good gate so he gets every chance to shine. ELNAJEEB (2) on debut is worth keeping tabs on, although the wide draw makes it harder.
